(define/contract (count-subarrays nums k)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let* ([max-num (apply max nums)]
         [positions (for/list ([i (in-range (length nums))]
                               #:when (= (list-ref nums i) max-num))
                      i)]
         [n (length positions)])
    (if (< n k) 0
        (let loop ([i 0] [count 0])
          (if (< i (- n k))
              (let* ([start (if (= i 0) 0 (- (list-ref positions i) 1))]
                     [end (+ (list-ref positions (+ i k -1)) 1)]
                     [prev-start (if (= i 0) 0 (list-ref positions (- i 1)))]
                     [next-end (if (= (+ i k) n) (length nums) (list-ref positions (+ i k)))]
                     [add (* (- end start) (- next-end end))])
                (loop (+ i 1) (+ count add)))
              count)))))
